INSERT INTO app.project_features (
                            project_id,
                            collection_id,
                            name,
                            added_by,
                            last_updated_by,
                            is_primary,
                            geom
                            )
                            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $4, COALESCE($5, false), ST_GeomFromWKB($6, $7)) RETURNING id AS "id: FeatureId"
